      "name": "Bench-scale hemolysis index comparison across 5 operating points",
      "description": "CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against in-vitro measurements at 5 flow-speed combinations. Mean absolute error 0.0031 g/100 L; all predictions within experimental uncertainty band at 95% confidence. Validation data sourced from FDA benchmark dataset."
