      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must be under configuration management with documented version control, regression testing, and traceable build records consistent with MRL 5 requirements.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 deployed under ISO 9001-certified QMS. Full regression suite (1 200 test cases) executed at release; build hash recorded in simulation log. Configuration management audit trail complete. Achieved level 4 meets required level 4."
