      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate order-of-accuracy verification on canonical benchmark problems relevant to rotating machinery and viscous hemolysis flows.",
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions applied to rotating-frame Navier-Stokes equations; observed order of accuracy 1.97 (expected 2.0). Taylor-Couette and lid-driven cavity benchmarks pass at published reference values. Code verification complete at required level 4."
    },
    {
