      "achievedLevel": 4,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) for NIH must be below 5% at the operating point producing maximum hemolysis.",
      "rationale": "Three-level Richardson extrapolation performed on structured hexahedral meshes (2.1 M, 8.4 M, 33.6 M cells). GCI for peak NIH = 2.8%. Iterative convergence verified to residual norm < 1e-6 at all operating points. Achieved level 4 satisfies requirement."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 4,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions must be documented with traceability to calibrated instrumentation and controlled fluid properties (viscosity, hematocrit) matching simulation inputs.",
      "rationale": "In-vitro tests conducted in temperature-controlled loop (37 ± 0.3 °C). Hematocrit 30 ± 0.5%, viscosity 3.2 ± 0.1 mPa·s verified by viscometry prior to each run. Flow rate and pressure controlled by calibrated Coriolis meter and transducers (NIST-traceable). Test conditions meet required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 4,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative agreement metric (e.g., E_rel) for NIH must be within experimental uncertainty at all 5 operating points; systematic bias must be characterised.",
      "rationale": "E_rel < 8% at all 5 operating points; maximum deviation 7.3% at highest flow rate. Systematic over-prediction of 2.1% identified and attributed to power-law hemolysis model constants. Bias within stated model uncertainty. Output comparison meets required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
