      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoI (NIH) must be the same scalar quantity used in clinical acceptance criterion; mapping from CFD shear stress history to NIH must be fully documented.",
      "rationale": "NIH computed via Giersiepen power-law model integrated along Lagrangian particle trajectories; identical formulation used in clinical threshold specification. QoI mapping documented in simulation plan. Relevance of QoI meets required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the validation activities to the COU",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
