      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry (identical to COU device). Five operating points span full COU flow-speed envelope (3–6 L/min, 2 500–3 500 rpm). Validation relevance meets required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Round-off and iterative solver errors must be shown to be negligible relative to discretization error; double-precision arithmetic required.",
      "rationale": "Simulations executed in double precision (IEEE 754). Iterative residuals converged to < 1e-6 for all equations. Round-off error estimated at < 0.01% of NIH, negligible relative to GCI of 2.8%. Solver error meets required level 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
