      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation setup must be reviewed by an independent analyst; boundary condition specification and post-processing scripts must be version-controlled and peer-reviewed.",
      "rationale": "Independent analyst review completed; 3 minor setup discrepancies identified and corrected prior to final runs. Boundary condition files and post-processing scripts committed to Git repository with peer-review approval records. Use error assessment meets required level 3."
