      "rationale": "Four independent batches of porcine blood analogue (30% hematocrit) used across test campaign. Inter-batch CV for NIH = 4.2%; incorporated into experimental uncertainty budget. Test samples assessment meets required level 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
