      "rationale": "Simulation boundary conditions set to experimental nominal values. Deviations: inlet flow rate ±0.05 L/min, rotational speed ±15 rpm. Sensitivity of NIH to these deviations bounded by ±0.0018 g/100 L (< 2% of NIH at worst point). Equivalency of input parameters meets required level 3."
    }
